    <item>
      <title>外国资金帮助莫迪推动印度债券销售创近纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/foreign-money-to-help-modi-push-near-record-india-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度被纳入全球债务指数之前，全球基金正在抢购印度主权债券，交易员预计这些债券将成为下一财年接近创纪录水平的政府借款需求的关键支柱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/foreign-money-to-help-modi-push-near-record-india-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国副财政部长表示关键利率“太高”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-25/thailand-s-deputy-finance-chief-says-key-rate-too-high-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国财政部副部长Julapun Amornvivat表示，该国基准利率“过高”，并敦促央行考虑放松货币政策。周三，他在香港亚洲金融论坛间隙与彭博社的大卫·英格尔斯发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-25/thailand-s-deputy-finance-chief-says-key-rate-too-high-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 01:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
